> ## Leo Group Bill Management System — Full Project Brief
>
> ### What This Is
> A full-stack web application for **Leo Group**, a pharma distribution company based in Thrissur, Kerala, India. They currently send 1500+ bills daily via WhatsApp which causes their number to get blocked. This system replaces that with a secure web portal where customers log in and download their own bills.
>
> ---
>
> ### Business Problem Being Solved
> - 1500+ bills sent via WhatsApp daily → number gets blocked repeatedly
> - No way to track who has paid and who hasn't
> - Manual follow-up for outstanding payments
> - No audit trail of bill delivery
> - Customers lose bills in WhatsApp chat history
>
> ### Solution
> - Customers get a portal login to access and download their own bills anytime
> - WhatsApp only sends a short notification link — never the file itself
> - Automated payment reminders fire based on configurable rules
> - Customers submit payment proof (GPay/NEFT screenshot + UTR) through the portal
> - Admin verifies proof and marks bills as paid
> - Full audit trail of everything
>
