> ### User Roles — Exactly 3
>
> | Role | Access |
> |---|---|
> | `admin` | Full dashboard — customers, bills, approvals, reminders, reports |
> | `customer` | Customer portal — their own bills only |
> | `marketing_company` | Customer portal — same as customer |
>
> - After login, backend returns the role
> - Admin → redirected to `/dashboard`
> - Customer and marketing_company → redirected to `/portal`
> - Registration requires **admin approval** before the user can log in
> - Pending users get HTTP 403 with message `"Your account is awaiting admin approval"` — not 401
>
