>
> ### Bill Formats — Per Customer Preference
> Every customer has one saved preferred format: **PDF**, **CSV**, or **Excel**.
> - PDF — generated from a template using DomPDF, or admin uploads a pre-made PDF
> - CSV — admin uploads a CSV file
> - Excel — admin uploads .xls or .xlsx file
> - All files stored on Cloudflare R2
> - Download links are **signed URLs valid 15 minutes** — never public
> - Customer portal shows exactly **one download button** per bill matching their preference
> - Admin can change a customer's preferred format anytime from their profile page
>
