> ### Database Schema — All 6 Tables
>
> **users**
> ```
> id, name, username, email, phone, password,
> role ENUM(admin, customer, marketing_company),
> status ENUM(active, pending, rejected),
> timestamps
> ```
>
> **customers**
> ```
> id, user_id (FK → users),
> customer_code (unique, assigned by admin),
> gstin (nullable),
> credit_limit (decimal),
> preferred_bill_format ENUM(csv, excel, pdf),
> salesperson_id (nullable FK → users),
> timestamps
> ```
>
> **bills**
> ```
> id, customer_id (FK → customers),
> invoice_no (unique), bill_date, due_date,
> subtotal, gst_total, grand_total,
> status ENUM(unpaid, overdue, paid),
> payment_status ENUM(unpaid, payment_submitted, proof_rejected, paid),
> payment_method ENUM(gpay, neft) nullable,
> utr_number nullable,
> proof_screenshot nullable,
> payment_submitted_at nullable,
> payment_verified_at nullable,
> rejection_reason nullable,
> bill_file_url nullable,
> bill_file_type ENUM(csv, excel, pdf) nullable,
> uploaded_by (nullable FK → users),
> timestamps
> ```
>
> **bill_line_items**
> ```
> id, bill_id (FK → bills),
> product_name, hsn_code nullable,
> qty, unit nullable, rate, gst_pct, line_total,
> timestamps
> ```
>
> **reminder_rules**
> ```
> id,
> trigger_type ENUM(before_due, on_due, after_due, weekly_overdue),
> offset_days, send_time,
> channel ENUM(whatsapp, popup),
> message_template nullable,
> is_active boolean,
> timestamps
> ```
>
> **reminder_logs**
> ```
> id, bill_id (FK), customer_id (FK),
> rule_id (nullable FK → reminder_rules),
> channel ENUM(whatsapp, popup),
> status ENUM(sent, failed),
> sent_at nullable, error_msg nullable,
> timestamps
> ```
