> ### Non-Negotiable Decisions — Final, Do Not Change
> - No Tailwind — vanilla CSS only
> - No SMS — WhatsApp only
> - No payment gateway — GPay and NEFT, manual proof submission
> - No public file URLs — always signed 15-minute URLs
> - No PDF sent over WhatsApp — text link only
> - No multi-tenant — Leo Group only
> - No third-party WhatsApp provider — Meta Cloud API direct
> - Bills are PDF, CSV, or Excel — one format per customer, never mixed
> - Outstanding amount = sum of all bills where payment_status is unpaid or proof_rejected
> - Customer code assigned by admin — not auto-generated
> - Registration always requires admin approval — no instant access
> - 3 roles only: admin, customer, marketing_company